---
source: tests/e2e/scarb/check_diagnostics.rs
description: "// → Scarb.toml\n[package]\nname = \"syntax_error\"\nversion = \"0.1.0\"\nedition = \"2025_12\"\n\n// → src/lib.cairo\nfn main() {\n    let x =\n}"
expression: "diagnostics_report(&mut ls, &[\"src/lib.cairo\"])"
